languages.text: "Экая ты ретивая, а. Хотя могу тебя понять: со всеми предущими твоими сородичами как-то... не задалось".
"You're antsy, aren't you? Though I can understand why — things didn't work out very well with the rest of your kin."

languages.text: “你很焦虑不安，对不对？不过我能理解这是怎么回事，你剩下那群族人恐怕不太顺利。”
languages.original_text: "You're antsy, aren't you? Though I can understand why — things didn't work out very well with the rest of your kin."

languages.text: « Ça vous angoisse, hein ? Enfin, c'est compréhensible. Il faut dire que vos semblables n'ont pas eu beaucoup de chance. »
languages.original_text: "You're antsy, aren't you? Though I can understand why — things didn't work out very well with the rest of your kin."

languages.text: «Tienes prisa, ¿no? Aunque lo entiendo. Las cosas no han acabado muy bien con el resto de tu gente».
languages.original_text: "You're antsy, aren't you? Though I can understand why — things didn't work out very well with the rest of your kin."

languages.text: 「不安でたまらないのね。その理由はわかるけど…あなたのキンの生き残りとは、全然うまくいかなかったじゃない」
languages.original_text: "You're antsy, aren't you? Though I can understand why — things didn't work out very well with the rest of your kin."

languages.text: "Ihr seid nervös, nicht wahr? Aber ich kann das verstehen. Die Dinge mit Eurer Verwandtschaft haben sich nicht gut entwickelt."
